Privacy Policy — Roadtrip Muse

Last updated: May 29, 2026

Roadtrip Muse ("the App") is operated by Christina Buoninfante. This policy explains what information the App collects and how it is used.

Information We Collect

The App does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information. Route preferences and saved places are stored locally on your device only and are never sent to any server.

Third-Party Services

The App uses the following third-party services, each subject to their own privacy policies:

• Apple MapKit & Apple Maps — used for location search, route planning, and points of interest. Subject to Apple's Privacy Policy at apple.com/privacy.
• Open-Meteo — used to fetch current weather conditions. No personal data is sent. Subject to Open-Meteo's terms at open-meteo.com.
• Google Maps / Rome2Rio / Amtrak — accessed via external links only. The App does not share data with these services.

Location Data

The App does not access or track your device's GPS location. Location names are entered manually by the user.

Children's Privacy

The App does not knowingly collect information from children under 13.

Changes

We may update this policy from time to time. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance.

